---
---
<section class="relative w-full min-h-[95vh] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-4 overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-16">
  <!-- Interactive Background Mesh/Gradient -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0F172A] to-[#050810] z-[-2]"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] md:w-[800px] md:h-[800px] bg-[#00C2FF] opacity-15 rounded-full blur-[120px] md:blur-[150px] z-[-1] mix-blend-screen pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center z-10 hero-content">
    
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-[#00C2FF]/30 bg-[#00C2FF]/5 backdrop-blur-md mb-8">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#00C2FF] animate-pulse"></span>
      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-[#00C2FF] uppercase tracking-wider">Nova Cloud Systems</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-8 font-syne tracking-tight text-balance">
      Transformamos la tecnología en tu <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00C2FF] to-[#F97316]">mejor modelo de negocio.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mb-12 leading-relaxed font-dm-sans text-balance">
      Integramos IA, automatización y ecosistemas cloud en soluciones llave en mano. Dejá de pelear con herramientas técnicas y empezá a escalar tus ventas sin sumar fricción a tu equipo.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-center w-full justify-center">
      <a href="#onboarding" class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#050810] font-bold text-lg rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-95 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,194,255,0.4)] text-center w-full sm:w-auto">
        <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          Agendar Sesión de Diagnóstico 
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
        </span>
      </a>
      
      <a href="#soluciones" class="px-8 py-4 text-gray-400 font-medium text-lg hover:text-white transition-colors text-center w-full sm:w-auto group flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        Ver nuestras plataformas 
        <span class="opacity-0 -translate-x-2 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-300">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-white/10">
      <span class="text-[#F97316] text-lg">★</span>
      <p>Más de <strong class="text-white">50 empresas</strong> ya operan en piloto automático.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { gsap } from "gsap";
  
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
    gsap.fromTo('.hero-content > *', 
      { y: 40, opacity: 0 },
      { y: 0, opacity: 1, duration: 1.2, stagger: 0.15, ease: 'power3.out', delay: 0.1 }
    );
  });
</script>
